{
  "stem": "14552.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother was in the-- my brother told me that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't remember it years ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He told me my mother was in the women's association.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I remember going with her to the hospitals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she would take food every Saturday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She would take over to the hospitals challah and the-- whatever goodies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was from the organization that they organized that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so she was very charitable, but in a-- charitable in the way that don't tell that you give.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because once you told, you no longer gave charity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then you gave yourself a present.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So give quietly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't let anyone know that-- and don't shame anybody who puts their hand out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if they put their hand out, they shame themselves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they must, they will do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if they are comfortable and they still want it, don't shame them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they have a reason for doing that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So a charity-- she understood charity for what it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, there was the chanting of the prayers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and, and the singing took place mostly between Saturday afternoon before the sun set, and the lights were not to be put on yet, and the [NON-ENGLISH] was about to be lit.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was this two hour between this quiet and dark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then my father would sing in the dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would all join him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the time I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he would sing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When he would be working, he would also sing, but not--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I, I-- you know, when you suddenly-- you-- it comes to you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- [NON-ENGLISH  SINGING].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was a song about a rooster who was in the forest, who has green feathers and red legs.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
